 BuidInDev - execute the pipeline for dev env and that include the code check, builds from development branch and deploy in dev env.
 BuildInSit execute the pipeline for sit env and enclude all checks, build from Release branch Deploy in SIT Env.
 DeployInProd - skip all stages and reads prod-configMapFIle from Git and deploys in production with lates image(code changes)


*/
